{"hash":"499d0acdb60fd13e5c28c9817b15999f21ae23a4","data":{"post":{"title":"Phalcon 1.3 : installation et configuration","date":"22 June 2014","content":"<p>Phalcon est un framework PHP ayant la particularité d'avoir son moteur écrit en Zephir ce qui le rend plus rapide que les autres framework PHP traditionnels. En effet, Zephir est un langage open-source de bas niveau conçu pour faciliter la création d'extensions PHP en les compilant en langage C.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 554 765' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-eab1b8e24f44f48d94f48436d571c588'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-eab1b8e24f44f48d94f48436d571c588)' width='554' height='765' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2btKpWT09n3GY7yrrH61Iz5GifI0AR2rJ7fYfWVVmwrIe8J55tOR36CrV089usVvT5GtPMXpx%2bJvbwN6zbsrdCSY1aQTFak27IxuyuO3F5bWym03Fwy0pyQgLWElUdYnrWbVwy6opadbWobkJUCRUFwplE8VcN2uSftgwp7VCUqkp3jZX%2bql2LFlh3mN6wfDWSPwrZxcJOLzRkZKSuh5xxaXUJSypaT1UFABNZyfumsHC6Ft8tKCme2SYIHlWe/h%2bdKMEn7pok/dNEnwH40hWAQCUgnoCetACyfumoji4n9lcxsfsjv0Gq/d%2b0fG29jmbo212pOLuU2rwAEqUVESnfp2TUXm%2bKru9zOdw3LaFh8FXdJMduS2DBP/auylhaukm1a23h8ohOtC1k8yY9j39vsZ6L%2bo1dKpfse/t9jPRf1GrpU8X18/F8RqHVx8EYOBwrRy1JCQe0CJJHlUHkUZR21umzkFY86xyrhu3SspEnaCTPduRU/RUE2ndFGrlKusDdP5Z6/eyd4bd%2b091UmBy90xzNE9e/pUda8DtG14dat8i%2b%2bjEXJeCy0ElRKkmFAnpt3V0airLE1UrJ85e4joweaObX/ALPG37DPWqL64c%2bKXqbl0pbSktFJUqBJgjtU47wzbKyt3fi/dFzc48Y9VuWflGlKNWrpO0%2bFdForXi6z%2b7nZ8IzUU93PLILgrDnAcP2%2bNKnFhiQFL0yZM9xjvqdooqMpOcnKWbKJKKshFGBsJ7qqmMaxuSu7xrH5N1560d0PITqHLXJ2M7HcflVrVMbCTIrk3A%2bYs8Fk%2bOb/ACThatkZHSpQSVQSpcbCrUaGthJrNWt5uxOpU0JRXYy/uYJK%2btw/vIVBgGfKYrZTiLMN6C26e8kurn6q3bd5NxbtvNGW3EhaT0kESKd38q5ypofDLXUSWnCSZ/iK/Wlaxts2tC0NuakmRLijv/s1vb%2bVG/lQBp31%2bmzLfMZeUhUytIGlER8xJETO1O2d03dtqW0ZS