<code class=\"language-text\">extension=php_falcon.dll</code>  </li>\n<li>Faites de même pour celui d'Apache : \"C://bin/apache/Apache2.4.4/bin/php.ini\"</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Démarrez (ou redémarrez) votre serveur WAMP.<br>\nEn faisant un <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;?php echo phpinfo(); ?&gt;</code>, on voit que l'extension \"phalcon\" est chargée.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 603 306' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-ea07a89d890a79cd9ca8546e2e7c7969'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-ea07a89d890a79cd9ca8546e2e7c7969)' width='603' height='306' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bmu%2bUFzCeLhrbuMQMAudJ0y/z01vWCOnkWzceUrvsPznupddMZhrqttWPti3S2lSUw%2btIAMTuEdArN4O7bQPpS4pqwJbM7jhlIX8FCivGF56lj/Z/5R8EdPJLH9vubVu4TwS2qRnjNLy1TGms1LG7YO4XJ925807uFy/2KzWIut4ZaLhbspAI3JYk6xpFDque0KlApb2byz6TBmP9FV5ccIqqp7kTNg3tW%2btAUq2lBPolyY%2bAqflS77B857qxi7vfFLWhhqwBaSN7mHOWI5iBrU2rnf8AOeGb2dyRuyMGZ94rP2fUESslPMlvlD17X1VdhW2nVuoW800Txt7japA3nQ%2b/fVSH0pSSpS4BHq1fTXS6FJPH5uqe7WukhR1g38HhGi2080kgjPD0SqOcTupiC4RIS7H51Uks3BkOKUQpG4DhEgkH9UfGmnCM9KOwjvqxMBVdysW90qS5HFmVmOUOndU0FzKmEu6D01UPdHGhgXCCmZTohM6joM1NLjOUb0adRHfXP6v3Ww0SphS/GGJGVzNAPLM6D30XLvVd7aqAYca8OxAlMQDyExoPxiis7PS32Ed9ZRj/2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"603\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/phalcon_extension_php_info.a691186.cb20ffd9ce22114cc53cd8bd62efc7d9.jpg 603w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 603px) 100vw, 603px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_extension_php_info.a691186.cb20ffd9ce22114cc53cd8bd62efc7d9.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_extension_php_info.a691186.cb20ffd9ce22114cc53cd8bd62efc7d9.jpg\" width=\"603\"></noscript></p>\n<h2>Téléchargement et installation de l'outil phalcon-devtools</h2>\n<p>A l'heure actuelle, en version alpha, le phalcon-devtools reprend le même principe que le Zend Tool pour ZendFramework, générer un nouveau projet, un nouveau contrôleur, un nouveau model, etc…<br>\nAllez à l'adresse : <a href=\"https://github.com/phalcon/phalcon-devtools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/phalcon/phalcon-devtools</a><br>\nOu via GIT : <code class=\"language-text\">git clone https://github.com/phalcon/phalcon-devtools.git</code><br>\nEditez le fichier \"phalcon.bat\" en modifiant la ligne suivante :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">set PTOOLSPATH=&quot;%~dp0/&quot;</code><br>\nPar le chemin correct où se situe \"phalcon-devtools\" :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">set PTOOLSPATH=C:/phalcon-devtools/</code><br>\nAjoutez dans la variable d'environnement \"Path\" le chemin de PHP et de phalcon-devtools : <code class=\"language-text\">;C:\\wamp\\bin\\php\\php5.4.12;C:\\phalcon-devtools</code> et validez.<br>\nTapez la ligne de commande ci-dessous :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">phalcon</code></p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 608 351' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-7aaf49b234849b93b9b3d78b457966bd'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-7aaf49b234849b93b9b3d78b457966bd)' width='608' height='351' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bYbZlZAtodUkFSVE7zT3oRtIt7s1mfI8UZSbQ56VM6tEyKuuHkrGEnEc4imV1iVKRLzBNaVKgc/GPOqSt0dMs10ma/ajbXZrP8Apq4oS5pOthxOFUtIU8ELH5RijqUrIUh2gO7EKwl0tE%2bqSsCvvGuUa4R0M09m3b0nWyhASmWkKDrQo/lCtqNtdms/6auKMFBDHHRc09m9OlC2TSsrZ%2bWf6auKHbDvvPWjeCz5d6TkUofmG21FCVAgVplyvGPPYt7n867H%2bLb%2b6I4Rt4ahXqKXUh9BKX5/D7SplwZ7vaO%2bOGgUo5FBqVdVdxz6%2bj/YbMyyzNTocUpKzMOUoDuxRXTT2N5RbUoIPRUgfKOiOL9LFCeUAQQupStIFRQdBP7boW5rEACXSkt5AYjkMuiKULWK0UoV30JjusXSmNVP5GBB%2bcoTioziJqS2qtYiwQQARb3P512P8W390VEW9z%2bddj/Ft/dEfhqP0j6is7RHdGcTMuzFksrccWFoVrHhhBSCQfWco1JNct%2b6Jmx%2b4jQSl2wUOLzqUzLyQf6xmCCKGjuyO4Pd0ebe4oNkdwe7o829xQQRRYNkdwe7o829xQbI7g93R5t7igggLEN/RLcgTbmCwkBpLOLAZh4nFXfXH1RCtXRxdKyG0TkhY6GppoBxpwPunCsZg0KiDBBBIkVZn//Z' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"608\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_options.e8fe0bf.5eb13cf759549df7db8e1842d018b2f3.jpg 608w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_options.e8fe0bf.5eb13cf759549df7db8e1842d018b2f3.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_options.e8fe0bf.5eb13cf759549df7db8e1842d018b2f3.jpg\" width=\"608\"></noscript></p>\n<p>On va s'intéresser à la commande \"project\" afin de générer un nouveau projet Phalcon.<br>\nPour cela, placez-vous dans le dossier de développement de Wamp :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">cd C://www</code><br>\nPuis lancez la commande \"create-project\" ci-dessous :<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">phalcon create-project mon_projet --enable-webtools</code><br>\nLes fichiers sont générés dans un nouveau dossier nommé \"mon_projet\".</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 608 255' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-8f64f4bb37842bada3e32822b410ed00'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-8f64f4bb37842bada3e32822b410ed00)' width='608' height='255' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bGrSO/Koa%2b7NQZehbl5dBFs2oB5xOYJ17R86ZKXXEqy2jfOJCIg/GudeUUaZZr4w4O8bHwUjouGamBz%2bqtHt4mOqaJXa4dlGuhUD81BSW3eKQLRsq55cvd7prR1t1wyLdKZUR1Exr7KtjjwZp9DlveLjyWU5bXDsvdOYn5qV3eRjzaSpVrhsD2Zj/qgMWj5/BV8KQWz2TOGlZYmY7qY48GafQ2O9DGTE2uH6a9hf1U9gW299iO0GH271lYpS/cNtqUhKwQJiR1vzrntS%2bx/3rwf92381Q4Rr4Xh7%2bilqQxeMTf3ZWH0kvudlskRmOtMpYTBzdIBnT1R1q9OA2rZt3weIQ8pDi/WK55EjTXqjTkIFSK/s%2bRtokJE8zmPxOtaIxa2UFSwmAVdIB1kcIn3UimBKsvHgCUy0dT/AFV%2b%2bO54vIVnHc8XkKaFFBuAjxXH8RpEsIk5jcATpDR1q/XHc8XkKzjueLyFNCjz/LLkmG3CO45DUtsg04NqsHJbWB0tvUpPiq7dwSq9dcJOcW8SDHJU8qh9rFKThqwFGFNQZM901FWhBuz/2Q==' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"608\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_create_project.e8fe0bf.c0201860712ff68b7370d939ea04f75d.jpg 608w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_create_project.e8fe0bf.c0201860712ff68b7370d939ea04f75d.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_devtools_create_project.e8fe0bf.c0201860712ff68b7370d939ea04f75d.jpg\" width=\"608\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Avec une architecture MVC classique :</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 608 511' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-36c9eb1b64c33449aa182cc1e68f633c'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-36c9eb1b64c33449aa182cc1e68f633c)' width='608' height='511' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bzds1nYyxga2mobD4scfuUt9HGubUHZu8SwSEtx6F6fZvDrQxo2vTUGzb%2b27xLU6ssck0qxrEYcSp6eNtNQvqozA1wJewtDQbk7OEUmk09z5yh0g6ln7zFHTjxo3CvUUsSF7WCGTEKwyuewNleLgXvwyFMyTxPkDIvKtJ9IX/wBbFxqgDX4hmaXDyz9gF/fK7yPcxx80fGR75c4cfwsV0Rxez5srXNeczDHfaG9Cgu9W6Ulgmc11hwbEHZ9FwQgIQhACae585Q6QdSz95iViae585Q6QdSz95ij0aj5IXFd67iFv5n98qzA%2bKWaQTRh73SZRxEqrX%2bu1/wDmf3yhkUnnecRvLQ%2b5IF0RHs8xANbPkbGGFosbcTulVVfqJWiia1knCc4h7ehUFSAhCEAJp7nzlDpB1LP3mJWJp7nzlDpB1LP3mKPRqPkhk0Oo3Aq01c76nEmSPkzMyVLbOa4BxLv09huTsF9ltquv1DaMFrBUVuMNfYgiKaMD/mLoQtINZIbwOiHPcc7aPwLzeB0P57jnbR%2bBCFeCBvA6H89xzto/AjeB0P57jnbR%2bBCE4BVm1D6LMqnsZV4uYmxZ7mePNe/9OKyv4Vq8wfQbz6uwqavknqaJ1ORPK1zcriCeJo%2bVCFj9%2bDNN59/Z/9k=' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"608\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/phalcon_mvc.e8fe0bf.7ad5be715834a9cbe8eb1158ac28f7dd.jpg 608w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_mvc.e8fe0bf.7ad5be715834a9cbe8eb1158ac28f7dd.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_mvc.e8fe0bf.7ad5be715834a9cbe8eb1158ac28f7dd.jpg\" width=\"608\"></noscript></p>\n<h2>Configurer l'accès à la base de données</h2>\n<p>Par défaut, Phalcon introduit le nom de la table concernée par le nom du projet (\"mon_projet\" dans notre cas).<br>\nPour le modifier, c'est très simple, ouvrez le fichier \"config.php\" présent dans le dossier \"app/config\" et éditez les lignes concernées.</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-php line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'database'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'adapter'</span>  <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'Mysql'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'host'</span>     <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'localhost'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'username'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'root'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'password'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'dbname'</span>   <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'mon_projet'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>Ensuite ces informations seront traitées dans le fichier \"service.php\" dans le dossier \"app/config\" (ligne 56).</p>\n<h2>Le WebTools</h2>\n<p>On accède au WebTools à l'adresse suivante : <a href=\"http://localhost/mon_projet/webtools.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost/mon_projet/webtools.php</a></p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 800 124' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-feba300953d51254e89bb09c55bcd0cd'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-feba300953d51254e89bb09c55bcd0cd)' width='800' height='124' xlink:href='data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bX8rcyrsOKAUbDipLK6Sq4JRgwGmhrrNTwo2HFTKuw4oBGaipuwB7GnZV2HFEKLjQUB//Z' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"800\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/phalcon_webtools.82a2fbd.f3b4b7d3b9382b7092d4924f1ecf20ea.jpg 480w, /assets/static/phalcon_webtools.775f9c8.f3b4b7d3b9382b7092d4924f1ecf20ea.jpg 800w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_webtools.775f9c8.f3b4b7d3b9382b7092d4924f1ecf20ea.jpg\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/phalcon_webtools.775f9c8.f3b4b7d3b9382b7092d4924f1ecf20ea.jpg\" width=\"800\"></noscript></p>\n<p>Vous pouvez désormais éditer vos controllers, vos models, le scaffold et les migrations (ces 3 derniers après avoir configuré l'accès à votre base de données) en vous passant des lignes de commandes...<br>\nOui mais n'importe qui peut se connecter sur cet outil de gestion en connaissant l'url ?<br>\nNon, car si vous allez dans le fichier de configuration de webtools, c'est-à dire \"public/webtools.config.php\", vous pouvez voir que l'accès à ce service est restreint ligne 30 :</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-php line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'PTOOLS_IP'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'192.168.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>Accéder au site</h2>\n<p>Pour accéder au site : <a href=\"http://localhost/mon_projet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost/mon_projet</a><br>\nPar défaut, c'est le contrôleur \"IndexController\" qui se charge de l'index du site<br>\nComment savoir quelle vue ce contrôleur charge ?<br>\nLe nom du contrôleur \"IndexController\" correspond au dossier \"index\"<br>\nLa fonction <code class=\"language-text\">indexAction</code> correspondant au nom du fichier de la vue \"index\"<br>\nLes vues étant par défaut chargées dans le dossier \"app/views (cf : app/config/config.php)\", on peut en conclure que le chemin est :<br>\n\"app/views/index/index.volt\"<br>\nEn ce qui concerne le layout, il se trouve à la racine du répertoire des vues :<br>\n\"app/views/layouts/index.volt\"</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>{{title}}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        {{ content() }}\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>La vue précédente, index/index.volt s'affiche par défaut dans la fonction <code class=\"language-text\">content()</code>.<br>\nPour charger la feuille de style de Twitter Bootstrap présente dans le dossier \"public\", placez cette ligne sous la balise title :</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>public/css/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>Phalcon permet via son outil de générer un projet rapidement malgré la configuration initiale qui peut sembler laborieuse pour les moins téméraires. Mais il ne déçoit pas au niveau performance et de son poids (moins d'1Mo du fait que le moteur du framework est présent dans le dll).</p>\n<h2>Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Site officiel de Phalcon PHP : <a href=\"http://www.phalconphp.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://www.phalconphp.com</a> ;</li>\n<li>Site officiel du langage Zephir : <a href=\"http://www.zephir-lang.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://www.zephir-lang.com</a> ;</li>\n<li>Cmder est une alternative à CMD et PowerShell (onglets et coloration syntaxique) : <a href=\"http://bliker.github.io/cmder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://bliker.github.io/cmder</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n","download":"","tags":[{"title":"Phalcon","path":"/tag/Phalcon/"}]}},"context":{}}